<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>内存 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98/</link><description>内存 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>ES磁盘不足与分片内存调优</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/bug%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5/es%E7%A3%81%E7%9B%98%E5%88%86%E7%89%87%E8%B0%83%E4%BC%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/bug%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5/es%E7%A3%81%E7%9B%98%E5%88%86%E7%89%87%E8%B0%83%E4%BC%98/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="es磁盘不足与分片内存调优">ES磁盘不足与分片内存调优</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Elasticsearch的稳定性高度依赖磁盘空间和JVM内存的合理规划，磁盘不足会触发只读保护导致写入中断，分片过多会耗尽堆内存引发OOM，通过索引生命周期管理、分片数量规划和水位线监控可预防此类问题。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="问题现象">问题现象</h2>
<p>线上ES集群出现以下异常：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl"># 现象1：写入被拒绝
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">cluster_block_exception: index [logs-2024-01] blocked by: [FORBIDDEN/12/index read-only / allow delete (api)];
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"># 现象2：节点频繁GC
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">[gc][23451] overhead, spent [2.1s] collecting in the last [2.3s]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"># 现象3：节点掉线
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Master node discovery: node-left reason: disconnected</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="影响范围">影响范围</h3>
<ul>
<li>日志写入失败，数据丢失风险</li>
<li>查询延迟飙升，影响检索功能</li>
<li>节点频繁掉线，集群稳定性下降</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="排查过程">排查过程</h2>
<h3 id="第一步检查集群健康状态">第一步：检查集群健康状态</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 集群整体状态</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">GET _cluster/health
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># status: red/yellow, unassigned_shards &gt; 0</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 节点磁盘和内存</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">GET _nodes/stats/fs,os,jvm
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># fs.total.free_in_bytes: 磁盘剩余</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># jvm.mem.heap_used_percent: 堆内存使用百分比</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第二步分析磁盘使用">第二步：分析磁盘使用</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 查看各索引占用空间</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">GET _cat/indices?v<span class="p">&amp;</span><span class="nv">s</span><span class="o">=</span>store.size:desc
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 发现旧日志索引占用了80%空间</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 查看磁盘水位线</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">GET _cluster/settings?include_defaults<span class="o">=</span>true<span class="p">&amp;</span><span class="nv">filter_path</span><span class="o">=</span>**.disk.watermark
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># low: 85%, high: 90%, flood_stage: 95%</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="第三步分析内存使用">第三步：分析内存使用</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 分片级别内存占用</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">GET _cat/shards?v<span class="p">&amp;</span><span class="nv">s</span><span class="o">=</span>store:desc
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 发现单个节点承载300+分片</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 段内存占用（Lucene底层）</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">GET _nodes/stats/indices/segments?filter_path<span class="o">=</span>nodes.*.indices.segments
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># memory_in_bytes 过大</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="根因分析">根因分析</h2>
<h3 id="磁盘不足根因">磁盘不足根因</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>因素</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>缺乏清理机制</td>
          <td>日志索引只增不减，无限累积</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>副本设置过多</td>
          <td>重要索引5副本，空间放大</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>无生命周期管理</td>
          <td>冷热数据未分离</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>水位线触发</td>
          <td>磁盘使用&gt;95%自动进入只读</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="内存不足根因">内存不足根因</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>因素</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>分片过多</td>
          <td>每分片都有堆内存开销，推荐单节点&lt;600分片</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>字段爆炸</td>
          <td>动态映射导致字段数失控</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>聚合查询</td>
          <td>大聚合占用大量内存</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>堆内存设置不当</td>
          <td>超过32GB无法使用CompressedOops</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="解决方案">解决方案</h2>
<h3 id="磁盘空间紧急恢复">磁盘空间紧急恢复</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 1. 释放只读限制（临时）</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">PUT */_settings
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="s2">&#34;index.blocks.read_only_allow_delete&#34;</span>: null
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 2. 删除过期索引（确认无用后）</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">DELETE /logs-2023-*
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 3. 收缩副本（临时释放空间）</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">PUT /important-index/_settings
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="s2">&#34;number_of_replicas&#34;</span>: <span class="m">0</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="索引生命周期管理ilm">索引生命周期管理（ILM）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-json">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-json" data-lang="json"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">PUT</span> <span class="err">_ilm/policy/logs_policy</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="nt">&#34;policy&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="nt">&#34;phases&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;hot&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nt">&#34;actions&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          <span class="nt">&#34;rollover&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            <span class="nt">&#34;max_size&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;50GB&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            <span class="nt">&#34;max_age&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;1d&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="p">},</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;warm&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nt">&#34;min_age&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;7d&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nt">&#34;actions&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          <span class="nt">&#34;shrink&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nt">&#34;number_of_shards&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="p">},</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          <span class="nt">&#34;forcemerge&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span> <span class="nt">&#34;max_num_segments&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="p">},</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;cold&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nt">&#34;min_age&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;30d&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nt">&#34;actions&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          <span class="nt">&#34;freeze&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="p">},</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;delete&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nt">&#34;min_age&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;90d&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nt">&#34;actions&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">          <span class="nt">&#34;delete&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="分片与内存优化">分片与内存优化</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-bash">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 1. 合理设置分片数</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 经验：单分片20-50GB，避免过小分片</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">PUT /new-index
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="s2">&#34;settings&#34;</span>: <span class="o">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="s2">&#34;number_of_shards&#34;</span>: 3,
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="s2">&#34;number_of_replicas&#34;</span>: <span class="m">1</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="o">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 2. 限制字段数</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">PUT _cluster/settings
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="s2">&#34;persistent&#34;</span>: <span class="o">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="s2">&#34;mapping.total_fields.limit&#34;</span>: <span class="m">1000</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="o">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 3. JVM配置</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># jvm.options</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">-Xms16g
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">-Xmx16g  <span class="c1"># 不超过32GB，留一半内存给Lucene文件缓存</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="监控告警配置">监控告警配置</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-yaml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c"># Prometheus规则示例</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">groups</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span>- <span class="nt">name</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">elasticsearch</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">rules</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span>- <span class="nt">alert</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">EsDiskHigh</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">expr</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">elasticsearch_filesystem_data_free_percent &lt; 15</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">for</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">5m</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">annotations</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">          </span><span class="nt">summary</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">&#34;ES节点磁盘不足&#34;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span>- <span class="nt">alert</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">EsHeapHigh</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">expr</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">elasticsearch_jvm_memory_used_bytes / elasticsearch_jvm_memory_max_bytes &gt; 0.85</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">for</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">5m</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">annotations</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">          </span><span class="nt">summary</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">&#34;ES堆内存使用率过高&#34;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span>- <span class="nt">alert</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">EsShardTooMany</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">expr</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">elasticsearch_indices_shards_total &gt; 600</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">annotations</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">          </span><span class="nt">summary</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">&#34;ES节点分片数过多&#34;</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="复盘与预防">复盘与预防</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>措施</th>
          <th>执行方式</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>容量规划</td>
          <td>按日增量<em>保留天数</em>（1+副本数）估算磁盘</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>强制ILM</td>
          <td>所有日志类索引必须绑定生命周期策略</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>分片审核</td>
          <td>新建索引Review分片数，避免默认5分片</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>定期ForceMerge</td>
          <td>只读索引定期合并段，减少内存占用</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>冷热分离</td>
          <td>热节点SSD、温节点SATA、冷节点可搜索快照</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
